{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"30d9eeb9bc","title":"为马毛姐题词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7b865f52e6","index":0,"year":1951,"month":10,"day":4,"articleId":"30d9eeb9bc"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji30","name":"毛泽东全集第30卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/30-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji30":{"comments":[{"id":"c54c57b0af","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"30d9eeb9bc","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为马毛姐写的题词。1949年4月20日夜，毛泽东、朱德命令中国人民解放军百万雄师强渡长江。年仅16岁的马毛姐在家乡安徽省无为县参加了渡江第一支船队，因战绩突出，被授予“渡江英雄”称号。1951年10月4日，毛泽东派人接马毛姐到家中做客，还特意为没有正式名字的小英雄“马四姐”起名为“马毛姐”。毛泽东说：“·马”是你家的姓，名字第一字就跟我姓了。当毛泽东知道马毛姐上学了，便高兴地在一本笔记本上写道：“毛姐：好好学习，天天向上。毛泽东一九五一年十月四日。”"}],"contents":[{"id":"830cd17dcb","type":"title","text":"为马毛姐题词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"30d9eeb9bc"},{"id":"c54c57b0af","type":"paragraph","text":"毛姐：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"30d9eeb9bc"},{"id":"8a6c0a1241","type":"paragraph","text":"好好学习，天天向上","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"30d9eeb9bc"},{"id":"06828c7dd4","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"30d9eeb9bc"},{"id":"42d3bf98da","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年十月四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"30d9eeb9bc"}],"page":{"id":"07226e6bd6","publicationId":"maoquanji30","articleId":"30d9eeb9bc","start":518,"end":518}}}},"__N_SSG":true}